{"tid":2514209,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"布林肯：香港並非中國內政  質疑金融中心地位","createTime":"2021-05-03T06:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T06:26:12.000Z","uid":227801,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae4a4b23df3a31f21044a7bda96b474620ef345","tid":2514209,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2021/05/cbs-60-minutes-interview-with-antony-blinken/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2021%2F05%2Fcbs-60-minutes-interview-with-antony-blinken%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOK0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=4b9484a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2021/05/cbs-60-minutes-interview-with-antony-blinken/</a><br />\n美國國務卿布林肯接受CBS訪問　　再提到香港、串爆指這並不是中國內政<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCBS新聞時事節目60 Minutes最近訪問了美國國務卿布林肯Antony Blinken，布林肯在節目中提到中國是外交政策中最大的挑戰，指中國在國內加強打壓，而在國際上則更加「戰狼」具侵略性。他亦提到香港與新疆事情，並串爆指這些並不是中國內政，指中國當年與英國簽署聯合聲明，現在明顯是違反有關聲明。<br />\n布林肯續指中國「有效地」打壓了香港的民主，沒有根據原本當年中英主權移交時的承諾，維持高度自治最少至2047。CBS主持Norah O&rsquo;Donnell問到，如何去處理香港問題時。布林肯指會確保打壓的人士不能去美國，並會實施制裁等行動。布林肯亦質疑香港是否能繼續維持國際金融中心地位，指香港人若不能投票，會透過腳去做實際行動。<br />\n布林肯在訪問中，亦再一次強調中國正對新疆進行種族滅絕（genocide）。他續指針對維吾爾族人士的多種行為，只是因為他們是維吾爾族人，布林肯認為這不只是違反美國的價值觀，而是國際的價值觀，所以美國會做一些事情，包括不准輸入以強制勞動去做的產品和制裁等。當CBS主持問到，為什麼不杯葛2022北京奧運的時候，布林肯指這不是他們目前關注的重點，因為還有一年。CBS再追問，「這有可能（杯葛）嗎？」，布林肯則指任何事情都可能發生（never say something impossible），只是目前不是關注的重點。"},{"pid":"88a7019fd244fbf8c05a8fae974c2a3256a91e1e","tid":2514209,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"會透過腳去做實際行動<br />\n冇lifeboat係咪要行路上廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33cc7531b5c295f3bb2d1ded82b991b725cc671","tid":2514209,"uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88a7019fd244fbf8c05a8fae974c2a3256a91e1e","tid":2514209,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"會透過腳去做實際行動<br />\n冇lifeboat係咪要行路上廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:14:52.000Z","msg":"問Ted cruz"},{"pid":"92d7cff33e5c591fe1be8409a62cb62cdbec8938","tid":2514209,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"又重新質疑過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要重覆loop幾多次"},{"pid":"99c251df55a892b89046a811bade9f5c7dbf46ef","tid":2514209,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"寸啲講白啲<br />\n香港唔係支那栽培管理既成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775d301cb1eb05ad3c06c382dec27754b9061b59","tid":2514209,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf97f0a9afad91d4dc16d2ab2c7099752ef34a59","tid":2514209,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec5d30d6951246cc85baea019e1e30d3750d593","tid":2514209,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce23ff10723bd74046598292139f3ab5602833eb","tid":2514209,"uid":59037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"布林肯篇講話咁撚多新聞，一邊就比人話奶共，一邊又可以比人覺得佢會搞9支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}